article_metadata.title: Fitness park debuts in Olathe | The Kansas City Star

og.description: The park, which opened June 5 in Heritage Park in Olathe, features exercise equipment that is designed to provide a full body workout. Johnson County provided the park and Olathe Medical Center paid the $45,000 to construct the fitness area.
